<h1>Email-Services</h1>
It provide email communication between different users.

This project displays three options to choose 
  1)NewUser (for new user who want to become a part of our email services)
  2)Login  (existing user want to login into their account)
  3) exit (to exit from Email Services)

After Login or NewUser User will see following options
  1)Compose Mail (to write a mail to user)
  2)Inbox (To see its Incomming mails)
  3)SentBox (To see its Outgoing mails)
  4)Trash (To see its Deleted mail from inbox)
  5)Logout (To Exit from current account)

When Inbox and SentBox are blank then they indicate that user has no message. 
